original: Bruun, Rolf Tage, civilekonom, Kalmar, f. 13/5/20 i Kalmar av konsul Tage B. o. Kerstin Gille. — Stud:ex. 39, HHS ekon. ex. 45. Utr. res. 37, 38, 39. Anst. h. A-B J. Bruun i Kalm. 39-40, åter där fr. 45. Hobby: tennis.
translated: Bruun, Rolf Tage, economist, Kalmar, b. May 13, 1920 in Kalmar, son of consul Tage B. and Kerstin Gille. — Graduated from high school in 1939, graduated from the School of Economics at HHS in 1945. Traveled abroad in 1937, 1938, and 1939. Employed by A-B J. Bruun in Kalm. from 1939-40, returned there in 1945. Hobby: tennis. No information on marriage or partners.
